name: Subiendo Solo
description:
For the production of this song I used the apps GarageBand and Beatmaker3 to create the instrumental, these apps are fundamental for every musical project I do but this time I had a lot more fun experimenting with crazy melodies and super cool and new sounds. I made the song with the intention of putting it in the car and spend it chilling with the girl (or your boy) 😉💙
